{"tid":2205343,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港青委託律師再遭逼退　家屬委託新律師接手","createTime":"2020-09-16T18:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T06:46:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0a10940a5850bf49f9c5342caef3e99ce5c57e29","tid":2205343,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:08:59.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】12名涉偷越邊境港人被扣押深圳鹽田區看守所至今已逾三星期，有關當局持續向家屬委託律師施壓，昨日再有一名律師被迫退出，但據悉家屬已成功委託新律師接手，繼續嘗試到看守所要求會見被扣港人。關注事件的抗爭派發起「十二手足中秋送暖行動」，周末起將擺街站派發明信片，再寄到看守所，希望港人以集體行動向當局施壓。<br />\n<br />\n有份協助12名港人家屬的泛民立會初選出線者鄒家成接受本報查詢時透露，昨日再有一名原來受家屬委託的內地律師受壓退出代理案件，令至今被迫退出的內地律師累計已增至五人。對於家屬委託律師接連被逼退，鄒家成指已成功再安排委託新律師，「12個家屬嘅律師都齊，雖然係搵到，但真係唔多（律師）夠膽接」，而家屬正不斷跟律師辦理公證等手續，讓律師可以繼續前往看守所求見被扣留港人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/B5WVPU5L2JGW3ODI7YGXGD2FRU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FB5WVPU5L2JGW3ODI7YGXGD2FRU%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BvsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=e46c14fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FB5WVPU5L2JGW3ODI7YGXGD2FRU%2F&h=f1394457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/B5WVPU5L2JGW3ODI7YGXGD2FRU/</a>"},{"pid":"d9011cddfd76ea90987b6d93e0b454300d48005c","tid":2205343,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88c0e54531444d43879b9606e799a0efb6d79f3","tid":2205343,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9011cddfd76ea90987b6d93e0b454300d48005c","tid":2205343,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no